org.cef.callback

Interface CefRunFileDialogCallback


  • public interface CefRunFileDialogCallback
    Callback interface for CefBrowserHost::RunFileDialog. The methods of this class will be called on the browser process UI thread.(CefBrowserHost::RunFileDialog的回调接口。此类的方法将在浏览器进程UI线程上调用。)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onFileDialogDismissed(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> filePaths)
      Called asynchronously after the file dialog is dismissed.(在取消文件对话框后异步调用。)

    • Method Detail

      • onFileDialogDismissed

        void onFileDialogDismissed(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> filePaths)
        Called asynchronously after the file dialog is dismissed. If the selection was successful filePaths will be a single value or a list of values depending on the dialog mode. If the selection was cancelled filePaths will be empty.(在取消文件对话框后异步调用。如果选择成功，filePath将是单个值或值列表，具体取决于对话框模式。如果选择被取消，filePaths将为空。)
        Parameters:
        filePaths - list of file paths or empty list.(filePaths-文件路径列表或空列表。)
